name: The Way of Seeing by Penyukata

metadata.name: Connect
metadata.description:
"Connect" is my way to connect with new people and anyone who likes this.

I want to bring anyone flowing with the feeling of being "connected", that I am telling a side of ourselves that sometimes tries to appear and show itself, something that has been locked up and held back for many reasons.  
Everyone feels it, it's part of our heart and it's been inside us all along, even when I made this, everything is still there, not just an alter ego.

but still connected.
